    "body" : "<p>If you use the <a href=\"http://code.google.com/p/guava-libraries/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Guava</a> library:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Set&lt;Foo&gt; set = Sets.newHashSet(list);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or, better:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Set&lt;Foo&gt; set = ImmutableSet.copyOf(list);\n</code></pre>\n"
