    "body" : "<p>You can convert <code>List&lt;&gt;</code> to <code>Set&lt;&gt;</code></p>\n\n<pre><code>Set&lt;T&gt; set=new HashSet&lt;T&gt;();\n\n//Added dependency -&gt; If list is null then it will throw NullPointerExcetion.\n\nSet&lt;T&gt; set;\nif(list != null){\n    set = new HashSet&lt;T&gt;(list);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
