      "body" : "I tried this one, <code>list.stream().collect(Collectors.toSet());</code> but IntelliJ suggested &quot;Can be replaced with &#39;java.util.HashSet&#39; constructor&quot;, so replaced with <code>new HashSet&lt;&gt;(list)</code>"
