    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Let's not forget our relatively new friend, <a href=\"/questions/tagged/java-8\" class=\"post-tag\" title=\"show questions tagged &#39;java-8&#39;\" rel=\"tag\">java-8</a> stream API.\nIf you need to preprocess list before converting it to a set, it's better to have something like:</p>\n\n<pre><code>list.stream().&lt;here goes some preprocessing&gt;.collect(Collectors.toSet());\n</code></pre>\n"
