    "body" : "<p>A more Java 8 resilient solution with <code>Optional.ofNullable</code></p>\n\n<pre><code>Set&lt;Foo&gt; mySet = Optional.ofNullable(myList).map(HashSet::new).orElse(null);\n</code></pre>\n"
